程序包 starray.java.mono4j.enums

Enum Class MonoGCRootSource

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<MonoGCRootSource>
starray.java.mono4j.enums.MonoGCRootSource
所有已实现的接口:
Serializable, Comparable<MonoGCRootSource>, Constable, CSharpEnum.CSharpEnumValue
public enum MonoGCRootSource extends Enum<MonoGCRootSource> implements CSharpEnum.CSharpEnumValue
Represents garbage collection root sources in Mono. Used by the profiler API when reporting root registration. Corresponds to the MonoGCRootSource in Mono's metadata/mono-gc.h
